node.title: Two dead following crashes in New Plymouth and Omaha
node.description: A teenager has died after being hit by a vehicle north of Auckland, and a person died following a crash in New Plymouth.
node.content:
["A teenager has died after being hit by a vehicle in Omaha, north of Auckland, and a person died following a crash in New Plymouth.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123RF\n
", "Emergency services were called to Omaha Drive, in the small beach community east of Warkworth, at about 4am this morning, where they found the boy's body.", "In a statement, police said the driver knew the teen, and is being questioned by serious crash investigators.", "In a separate update, police said a person died following a crash at 5am this morning in New Plymouth.", "A car hit a parked car at the intersection of St Aubyn Street and Calvert Road in Lynmouth.", "The road is still closed."]
